reviewText: Fantastic product and delivery time right on
LOVE ME SOME SOME WANDA SYKES,,HOPE THEY RELEASE  SEASON 2..FOX DROPPED THIS SHOW..MAKES ME WONDER..TOO FUNNY..GREAT CAST..GREAT WRITING..WANDA.PHIL MORRIS..TOO FUNNY
I loved this show. I can't wait for Season 2 to be put on DVD. I wish this show had not been cancelled. It was really funny.
Its a very funny tv and Wanda Sykes the comedian always makes me laugh.
I Hated that for a complete first season,that they only had 6 !/2 hour episodes.
I still don't understand why this was cancelled after two seasons!  It's hilarious.

Though it had a short-run "Wanda At Large" was funny, edgy, and a great breakthrough opportunity on a major network for Ms. Sykes.  It great to watch these episodes again and I hope Amazon offers the second season soon.
She is so funny I can't understand why there were no more seasons after this. This is so worth getting.
